"Who Is It" was spending its last week on the UK chart by then. It seems like it and "Jam" were released on the same day in different territories.

8 singles from Dangerous were released in North America, 9 outside of NA. The only one not to receive a NA release was Give In To Me. Epic premiered the music video on MTV U.S. and were ready to promote it, when MJ sang Who Is It in the Oprah interview, forcing Epic to change gears and promoting Who Is It to radio and retail. Curiously, Epic never sent the original music video to MTV and video outlets, instead opting to hold a contest for music fans to create a video.
